# 十、CustomerLifecycleStage（生命周期）

Customer 生命周期采用统一阶段。

```
Prospect

↓

Lead

↓

New Customer

↓

Active Customer

↓

Loyal Customer

↓

VIP Customer

↓

Dormant Customer

↓

Lost Customer
```

Lifecycle 由规则引擎计算。

不能人工指定。

---

